Fix PoDoFo 1.0.x API compatibility.

PoDoFo 1.0.x has significant API changes from earlier versions:
- PdfMemDocument constructor changed to Load() method
- GetPage() -> GetPages().GetPageAt()
- PdfRect -> Rect with direct member access
- ePdfDataType_* -> PdfDataType::*
- PdfStream -> PdfObjectStream with CopyTo()
- PdfVecObjects -> PdfIndirectObjectList
- GetIndirectKey() -> FindKey() on dictionary
- Various pointer-to-reference changes

